Naomi Klein - A Canadian Perspective on US Media
------------------------------------------------

Naomi Klein author of "No Logo" and producer of "The Take", an award winning documentary, addresses the US media. Interviewed by David Barsamian at the 2005 Media Conference in St. Louis.
